HTTP STATUS CODE

200 Satisfactory response OK
    201 CREATED
    202 ACCEPTED
300 Relocations
400 Errors Bad Request
    401 UNAUTHORIZED
    404 Not Found
500 => servidor: Internal server Error
    503 Service Unavailable
    504 Gateway Timeout => es un time determinado

